{"tid":1383017,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《冷氣哨兵攻略》","createTime":"2019-07-29T15:11:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T21:57:03.000Z","uid":161626,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"752841dde358bb889129b0456a6cc60da496b57d","tid":1383017,"uid":161626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:11:05.000Z","msg":"喺現場嘅手足冇可能睇晒十幾個TG Channel，睇得晒都消化唔到咁多咁亂嘅資訊，所以佢地需要有朋友做 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">冷氣哨兵</span></strong></span> ，喺屋企mon晒所有資料，篩選出最精簡，最有用嘅資訊俾佢地。上唔到前線嘅巴絲打可以參考依篇冷氣哨兵攻略，保護自己嘅前線朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 事前準備 </span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">1.1 約定溝通方法</span></span></strong><br />\n我係用Whatsapp，因為TG個app不時連好耐線都連唔到。如果對方Whatsapp唔會收到敏感訊息，更加可以請佢開喺lock screen預覽Whatsapp訊息 （然後關其他所有notifications)，務求佢一拎個電話出來就收到佢最需求嘅資訊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">1.2 約定支援時間</span></span></strong><br />\n要一早講定自己幾時得閒，最好係話「由晏晝四點開始，我會無間斷支援你直至你返到屋企」，如果途中要食飯，一係推咗佢，一係講到明自己由 xx:xx 至 xx:xx 唔得閒，記著喺前線任何時候都可能會有突發事件，有時甚至得幾分鐘去反應，你柯個屎都可能會令戰友身堪險境。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">1.3 約定被捕支援</span></strong></span><br />\n拎晒你支援緊嘅手足同佢現場隊友嘅中文姓名、英文姓名、身份證號碼、親人電話。約定「如果你連續xx分鐘失聯，我會假設你被捕，將你嘅資料交俾律師」。可以約定埋想搵邊個組織嘅律師幫手。亦可以問定「如果你被捕，你屋企有咩物品係需要清走嘅？」去預防搜屋。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">1.4 Follow / Bookmark 所有資訊頻道</span></strong></span><br />\n我比較信任嘅sources包括：<br />\nTG: 反送中已核實資訊頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/antiextraditionverifiednews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fantiextraditionverifiednews&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJbhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=c693d8cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/antiextraditionverifiednews</a><br />\nTG: Scott Scout 認證哨兵消息主頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/scottscout\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fscottscout&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJbhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=057372ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/scottscout</a><br />\nTG: 香港TG新聞及資訊廣播 HKTGB <a href=\"https://t.me/hktgb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhktgb&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJbhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=1f0bb139\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hktgb</a><br />\nTG: 612 reminder <a href=\"https://t.me/reminder612\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Freminder612&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJbhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=c4963920\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/reminder612</a><br />\nTG: 《背水一戰馬拉松路面目測》 <a href=\"https://t.me/juneforstfuneral\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjuneforstfuneral&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJbhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=352132dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/juneforstfuneral</a><br />\nTG: 青年新政 Youngspiration <a href=\"https://t.me/youngspiration\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyoungspiration&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJbhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=5c871155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youngspiration</a><br />\nTG: 中大學生會消息發佈 <a href=\"https://t.me/cusunews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcusunews&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJbhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=4f942f47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/cusunews</a><br />\nTG: 香港獨立媒體網 <a href=\"https://t.me/inmediahknet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finmediahknet&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJbhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=c651277c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/inmediahknet</a><br />\nTG: 鍵盤戰線頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/kbflF5c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FkbflF5c&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJbhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=c5a15791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/kbflF5c</a><br />\nTG: [反送中]Fact Check Channel <a href=\"https://t.me/antielabfactchecking\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fantielabfactchecking&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJbhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=85a1e45d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/antielabfactchecking</a><br />\nTG: 前線實時新聞直播 <a href=\"https://t.me/realtimenewsbroadcasts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frealtimenewsbroadcasts&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJbhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=9df0833b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/realtimenewsbroadcasts</a><br />\nTG: 民間人權陣線資訊頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FCivilHumanRightsFront&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJbhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=64651cbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront</a><br />\nTG: 港島交通台 <a href=\"https://t.me/islandalliance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fislandalliance&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJbhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=ef7d97a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/islandalliance</a><br />\n各大Facebook/電視嘅Live都非常有用，但要睇埋就要搵多個朋友幫手。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">1.5 睇熟地圖</span></span></strong><br />\n訊息支援唔係亂咁copy and paste，而係按照你戰友嘅位置篩選資訊俾佢。我經常要即場喺Google Map搵「西港城喺邊？」「元朗警署近元朗站定係朗屏站？」「安樂路喺邊？」「IFC離上環幾遠？」，令訊息支援慢咗，唔好同我犯同一個錯。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1.6 心理準備</span></span></strong><br />\n做冷氣哨兵，你身邊冇人可以幫你分擔壓力，情緒有機會比上前線同一大班人一齊更唔穩定。如果你支援緊嘅人係你老死，你可能會喺危險時刻變得極焦慮。但你要忍，冷靜、效率咁支援隊友，直至佢地返晒屋企為止。千其唔好將自己嘅焦慮傳染俾戰友，亦唔好喺chatroom講任何廢話，佢地唔需要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 訊息支援</span></span></strong><br />\n記著訊息支援唔係 copy and paste，冷氣哨兵嘅任務係篩選出最精簡，最有用嘅資訊俾戰友，如果你同戰友個chatroom同TG channel一樣咁亂，咁你只會幫倒忙。我會將戰友需要嘅訊息分成三類：緊急提醒、戰略概況、撒退方法。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2.1 緊急提醒</span></span></strong><br />\n緊急情況包括第一次黃/紅旗，頭幾次黑旗/催淚彈（煙好明顯，唔太需要你提醒），燈旗/開槍，速龍，包抄（，水炮車）。<br />\n<br />\n咁係咪「2303 西港城外 30 速龍突擊示威者（設計資訊）」就極緊急呢？視乎隊友位置。如果你隊友當時近IFC，你不斷send依啲即時訊息俾佢只會令佢對「緊急」麻木。所以你要掌握隊友位置，篩選剩佢近100米，甚至近50米嘅即時資訊俾佢地。情況愈危急，你隊友愈冇時間睇手機，你就愈要篩選你俾佢嘅資訊。<br />\n<br />\n其實前線最睇唔到嘅係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">包抄</span></span></strong>，喺上環打緊嘅手足唔會知道啲狗已經喺中環街市準備好包圍，亦有可能企後少少嘅人知道包抄之後走晒剩低班前線，所以緊急提醒之中最重要嘅係包抄，務必立即提醒，甚至打電話通知。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2.2 戰略概況</span></span></strong><br />\n香城online冇小地圖，需要靠你消化完大量資訊後總結個大局俾佢地聽。我建議嘅做法係開個word將所有TG channel嘅有關警察佈防/行動、警察武力等級、示威者人數、示威者行動嘅資訊按區分類，然後每10-15分鐘俾一個大update隊友。<br />\n<br />\n有時你睇得多會摸到雙方嘅行動意圖，倒如「示威者想由金鐘急速轉移去西環突襲中聯辦」、「警察正喺中環一帶集結上gear，好快會有一波清場行動」、「啲狗今次唔係想清場，而係想包抄大搜捕」，唔怕將你嘅推測分享俾戰友知。<br />\n<br />\n另外，TG Channel比較少報示威者人數、示威者行動，但當戰線一長，唔少後方手足會見唔到衝突，唔知道前線做緊啲咩，而前線手足亦唔知後兩條街重有幾多人，唔知有冇增援黎緊。所以提供我方資訊同提供敵方資訊係同等重要！講多次，提供我方資訊同提供敵方資訊係同等重要！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">2.3 現場撒退資訊</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你嘅戰友一日未同你講話要撒，佢都唔需要任何撒退資訊</span></span></strong>，所以千其唔好亂send一堆退場資訊打亂佢地。但都唔代表你唔洗收集撒退資訊！你要一得閒少少就收集以下三階段資訊，務求隊友一講「我依家撒」，你就可以按階段俾料佢。<br />\n<br />\n第一階段：離開hot zone<br />\nHot zone 通常冇地面交通，亦有時離地鐵站好遠，或者地鐵站封咗，你隊友喺依個階段需要一條冇狗嘅逃生路線，走去一個安全上交通嘅地方。依張圖係最好嘅例子（紫色路線）：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2211xb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2211xb.jpg&h=45b19628&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二階段：上交通工具<br />\n準備好(1)附近巴士站位置同巴士目的地，(2)附近咩地鐵站有狗，咩地鐵站安全（可能有埋車票同衫），(3)車隊接送資訊，等隊友一離開hot zone就send俾佢地。<br />\n<br />\n第三階段：轉車/落車/出閘<br />\n喺依個階段，隊友會頹晒/鬆懈晒，但你唔可以！過去地鐵站熱門轉車位（e.g.金鐘、中環、太子、旺角、油塘、南昌）都出現過狗，地鐵站出口（e.g 元朗、天水圍、荃灣、青衣，觀塘）又有，地面(e.g.朗豪坊、紅隧)更加唔洗講。辛苦少少，問清楚隊友回家路線，幫佢沿路睇實最新資訊，捱到佢地返晒屋企嘆冷氣，你嘅任務先完結！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">最後，最後，記著你只係冷氣哨兵，唔係冷氣軍師，唔好指指點點，提供完最準確嘅資訊，就請你信任隊友嘅決定，正如佢地信任你俾佢嘅資訊一樣。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"93ba6a76e86b0cd2e889126b34403a1531f07435","tid":1383017,"uid":2704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:11:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8eae01dfbb80cdb0f32f10dd23930ec9e64eec4","tid":1383017,"uid":161626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:14:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4c93c4f4e1c18b1d2b248732c84bc2488285bf0","tid":1383017,"uid":161626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:19:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d72cca64d7f4146733cca911a6bb89c5dc2563fa","tid":1383017,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:21:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推! 8月5罷工!!!!! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日(7月30)1500-2000</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">餓住的小朋友入一入黎, 有心幫佢地都可以黎睇下</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1382980/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1382980/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\nTG:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkrevolutiondocument&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsa